race.comment: SHY CABANG (5) comes off an average effort last start when sixth at Bendigo over 425m behind Raven Force (24.93) in a Grade 5. Has ability and can bounce back. LILLY LOUD MOUTH (1) has shown good improvement at her last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 2nd at Geelong over 460m. Can feature again. RED SHIRAZ (2) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at Bendigo in a handy 24.60 beating Bone Shaker. Bold showing expected again. PAW HULL (6) led and held on to fill a placing last start - in the mix again.
